  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK922">
<l>uṇṇaṟka kaḷḷai yuṇiluṇka cāṉṟōrā </l>
<l>leṇṇap paṭavēṇṭā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let no liquor be drunk; if it is desired, let it be drunk by those who care not for esteem of the great.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
